% Presburger solver ground-truth regression (BETA1 spec section 2.3).
% These four queries have unambiguous semantics over the naturals;
% any deviation indicates a bug in `Calc.Presburger.Internal`
% (the QE pipeline + truth-value evaluator).
%
% Expected:
%   ?- presburger "forall X, X = 0".   => no.   (X = 1 is a counterexample)
%   ?- presburger "forall X, X >= 0".  => yes.  (always true in nat)
%   ?- presburger "exists X, X > 5".   => yes.  (X = 6 witnesses)
%   ?- presburger "exists X, X = 7".   => yes.  (X = 7 witnesses)
